data.description: **Professional Photos coming 11/11** Experience the best of both worlds with this pristine 2-year-old manufactured home, set on a generous 3-acre flat lot within a desirable gated community in Aguanga. This property isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. The open floor plan is accentuated by high-end granite and quartz countertops in the kitchen, providing an inviting ambiance for entertaining and everyday life.    Step into the master suite where you'll find a sumptuous soaking tub in the master bathroom, alongside expansive closets designed to house your wardrobe with ease. An oversized 2-car garage offers extra room for your projects and storage needs.    As a resident, you'll have access to exclusive community amenities that cater to relaxation and recreation. Enjoy picturesque walking trails, community events in the clubhouse, and security that comes with living in a gated neighborhood. This home is a haven of peace and comfort in a community that adds value and enjoyment to your daily life. Welcome to your slice of paradise. **Qualifies for a low interest rate FHA Assumable loan**
